Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's case takes place in\Nthe Kagomma area of Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle gets a sampling of the finest Shochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the brewery smells of complicated human relations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through to the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.62,0:00:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I look like a child, but have the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:58.78,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kagoshima Nichiuri TV
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beer is definitely the best form of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Refrigerate it, put it in a mug, and chug it all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There^s nothing that can beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt's deliciousness comes from its bitterness and.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, our topic is on alcohol, but beer is the wrong kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NUm, our topic is on alcohol, but beer is the wrong kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't I supposed to speak passionately about alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:24.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tokuzumi Yuka\NKagoshima Nichiuri TV Announcer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:24.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're talking about the alcohol that's\Nbooming in popularity these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Ohl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 see... Well, wine is just splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I know the benefits of the polyphenol...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Err, not wine...\NEven I know the benefits of the polyphenol...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is a special program celebrating\Nthe station's anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:38.93,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kondo Yousuke\NKagashima Nichuri TV Director
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:38.93,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yoshidemo Shougo\NKagashima Nichuri TV Productor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why did we invite such a stupid guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he's famous and likes to drink sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd think that this guy would get a clue\Nfrom hearing the word "sake" in Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The announcer lady is crying, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whats with These murderous star es?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to Kagoshima and .
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kagoshima a ft sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beer is good! Wine is also great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my absolute favorite is Shochu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I wanted to give a comparison so\Npeople can understand the greatness of Shochu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you talked about\Nother alcoholic beverages first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.73,0:03:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! So t/iat's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I, Mouri Kogoro, cannot hide it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I especially have to say that the Shochu\Nthat's brewed right here in Kagoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the absolute best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banzai for Kagoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ali right! Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} saved the show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were right to invite him, weren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He fooled them somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give him credit for that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you say 'Takakuma"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about that rare\Ntype of Shochu, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The product is made in limited\Nquantities, so it's very hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Do I get to sample it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I asked Kuramato, he said it'd\Nbe a pleasure to serve some to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Catch the ferry here in Kagoshima,\Nand it'll take you right to Tanimizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get to drink it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rare Takakuma Shochu that most can only dream about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we boarded, little did we know\Nof the gruesome case that awaited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:44.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Gets Drunk in Satsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:44.50,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Bölüm 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takakuma Brewery... I guess this is where it's made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a clear view of the ocean, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this is the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.85,0:05:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi Satoshi(30)\NTakakuma Brewery Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome. I'm Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard your name mentioned quite frequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.15,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi Fumiko (27)\NSatoshi'nin Karisi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his wife, Fumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My daughter, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this freeloader...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy, I don't think cellars full\Nof bottles will interest you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're very lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Mt. Takakuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. So that's where the name came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think of the Takakuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing. Ali I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:05:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is the best I've ever tasted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simply exquisite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all take allot of pride in brewing this sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sake-brewing process\Nbegins by washing and steaming rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we add koji mold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Note: Koji is a special type of, mold which releases\Nenzymes that help break rica down into carbon dioxide and alchol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the koji is ready, we\Ntransfer it into an earthenware pot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Add water and yeast to ferment it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we add steamed sweet potatoes to ferment it further.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During that time, we continue mixing\Nto maintain a constant temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to stop various bacteria from multiplying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, we distill it and let it rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dilute it with water...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some facilities us e machines to\Nbrew it, but our sake is handmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt may seem like bragging when\Nwe call it a "limited" product, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't make too much.\NWe're already making as much Shochu as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Local, handmade... This is the real thing right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last week, I requested permission to do a report here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Maezono, from the Weekly Etta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Report?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ee... May I see the managing director, Tatsumura-sari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:22.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maezono Hitomi (25)\NMagazine Journalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did everyone react to the name Tatsumura?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.77,0:07:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to film the brewing process.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brevving process?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} agreed to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What the hell was he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He selfishly made a stupid promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, we cannot show\Nthe brewing process to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's very important that we keep\Nthe area free of any outside bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we cannot let non-employees in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true. There are many germs on the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's common sense, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I love Shochu, so I accepted the task of doing the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know asking would make you so upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We re just pissed off at that Tatsumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what a re you yelling for Kosugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:26.85,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura Shinsuke (45)\NTakakuma Brewery Managing Director
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my... Looks like I'm not welcome here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you Maezono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Evet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. I'm late for your interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My physical checkup took longer than I\Nexpected, thanks to a certain someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the small size of this place surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we re thinking of<remodeling this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making everything machine-run so\Nwe can mass produce our product...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're planning to do that to Takakuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mass production?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you promised us that you'd never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we mass produce Shochu, its quality will suffer greatly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the president is very stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't cash in on the recent\NShochu boom, what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, l!m also against mass producing the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,II talk with my manager and\Nhave him reconsider doing this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Özür dilerim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,II let you take a bottle Home! We need the advertising!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show more love and respect for your sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't even care about tainting the Takakuma name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if bacteria didn't go near the sake,\Nthere's already enough scum here to ruin it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scum? Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's wrong with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm also against stopping the handmade process.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and thank you very much for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:05.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! The famous detective, Mouri Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The personality for your brand's image?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A famous person promoting us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you accept, you can drink as\Nmuch of our sake as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Unlimited Takakuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, a re you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sake is too tempting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! How about I show you around town tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I II be off, and we can get some great food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it'll all be on me, so please consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.97,0:10:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:54.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it as my thanks for enjoying our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me have the honor of being your tour guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him, I guess a woman would make it more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let the mistress be the tour\Nguide and I'll just relax tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, III be expecting an answer from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Why didn't you say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Saigo Takamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:34.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Note: Saigo Takamori was one of che most influential samurai in Japanese history, famously known as "The Last True Samurai."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop changing the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I've got a bad feeling about Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone else seemed to dislike him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not just disliked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's utterly despised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why do Shiraishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and his wife keep him on the staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're giving a report on the wind direction\Ncoming from Sakurajima, even though this is Kagoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind often blows ash\Nhere all the way from Sakurajima...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it'd be a pain if ashes blew\Nonto your laundry while it was hanging outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! So that's why people are so\Nworried about the direction of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will there be ashes coming today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's completely random.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! How did they write that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you and your husband just fire Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you little. .!.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:13:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course a chi 1 would be curious. But I can't fire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of an old promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our sake plant has a history that goes back for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't very big or well-known back\Nthen, so we couldn't sell as much as we had hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would have shut down a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luckily for us, Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a salesman at\Nthe time, worked very hard to help sell our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, we still couldn't produce as\Nmuch as the other big sake companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were about to be shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was ten years ago, five years before İ got hired there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the former managers father spoke with\Nthe workers who were still in training and made a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:14:02.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said, "If this is the last batch of sake we'll make,\Nwhy not get the finest ingredients and make it perfect?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the best, most ideal sake would be\Ntheir final memory of the Takakuma Brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that became Takakuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and then we got to see our dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone lined up to get a taste of the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But last year, the former manager became deathly ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about the decision we made ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} started to change after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What Mass production?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:35.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People a re only buying Takakuma for the brand name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it loses its taste a little,\Nwho would notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Business, business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to let him get away with that, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of letting him ruin the sake,\Nwe should kick him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for him, we wouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're in his debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I can never forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a very stubborn person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe "loyal" is a better word?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never forgetting a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of a man from Satsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:14.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please decline the offer from Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone as famous as you helped him advertise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt would be like making him invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt would only help him carry out\Nhis plan of mass producing our sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be why you wanted to\Ngive us a tour today—to convince me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine! I was going to reject his offer anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s house is in Kagoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, good. İt looks like he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six o'clock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you taste something weird in your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No w that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt has to be all the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that it's Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can deduce what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was resting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the circumstances, it's definitely a kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys said the lights were on when you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means he must have been\Nkidnapped sometime in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I tested it, I noticed that the blood wasn't dry yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means he was killed shortly before 6:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otakeyama, get the car ready immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the nurse who used\Nto work at the Chuo Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That was five years ago, before I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you looked familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:12.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for involving you in such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's still worried about him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 guess it's because even though Takamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nis ill-natured, he's the savior of the brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the motive was money, the\Nculprit will contact us with their demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when we'll catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, there was no\Ncontact from the culprit the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why won't he contact us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another day passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an anonymous phone call to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We traced the call to Terayama Park in Kagoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:19:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt looks people wouldn't typically come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The phone call%as most likely from the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, their voice was masked,\Nso we couldn't determine their gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kidnapped and then murdered, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been two days since he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy\Nreport, he died about two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's hard to determine the\Ntime of death accurately after two days...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believe he was killed sometime\Nduring the evening he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt appears to have been an instantaneous\Ndeath, caused by a single blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding the statue lying in the living room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've verified that the shape of\Nthe wound matches it perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:46.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood was on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we can safely assume that it was the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His death was instantaneous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the culprit didn't knock Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nunconsious and then kidnap him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that they killed Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on the spot,\Ndrove his body to the park, and just left him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then called us two days later to tell us where to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were they trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They took the time to move the body elsewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then told us exact!y where to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, according to our investigation team...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s doors and windows\Nshowed no signs of forced entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the key is special and cannot be duplicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how did the culprit enter the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İn other words, Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knew the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this case, no money was\Nstolen, so the motive wasn't robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only other possible motive is revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:21:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was an acquaintance of\NTatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who hated him enough to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The culprit is one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who knew Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Na re those involved with this brewery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why am I a suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The others heard you voice your hostile\Nfeelings towards him when you came to do a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that we all hated Tatsumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was murdered two nights ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, we were in the back room making a new batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.39,0:21:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,İt's possible that all of you\Nmatched your stories beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for you, Maezono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were staying at a hotel by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you do not have an alibi, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to suspect all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Shinpuku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is right. Any of you could have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True. No one here has a sol d alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.58,0:22:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And everyone despised Tatsumura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone close to her is under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:31.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is most likely still here in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sake is filled with living organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.22,0:24:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you start making it, you can't\Ntake your eyes off of it for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why none of us could have left during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I looked into what you asked me,\Nand there wasn't even a trace on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, well... The culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.82,0:24:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you know who did it, go stand\NV in front of everyone and tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:30.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Gets Drunk in Satsuma
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:30.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Gonan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Physical Checkup
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gelecek Bölümde Göürüşürüz!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, well have a really wild conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.75,0:24:38.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.62,0:24:39.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Dad!
